file_content.text: Bipedal eradication of Killik green perpendiculars progresses quickly. Report transmission should safely resume within a mere two thousand local system revolutions. Journey in purple tangent!
Tread subtly, chosen of Gray Secant! Killik green perpendiculars are active in this region. They must not intercept observational data reports!
The Killiks will inflict your mind with yellow nonagon! Avoid them!
